              By virtue of MPI the MPI_Recv call should only return
              messages destined for that rank.&nbsp; What makes you think
              that is not happening?&nbsp; Can you make some sort of kernel
              of code that proves your theory that your MPI_Recv is
              receiving another rank's message?&nbsp; If you can and then
              post that code maybe we'll be able to figure out what the
              issue is.<br>
              <br>
              Right now, it seems we are at a deadlock of you claiming
              something is happening that really cannot be happening.&nbsp;
              So unless we have more than a broad description of the
              problem it is going to be nearly impossible for us to tell
              you what is wrong.<br>
